body:
The PR #19582 moved built tracks MultiTrackValidator instance from trackingOnly sequence to the standard sequence, but accidentally did not update the summary harvesting configuration. This PR fixes that by moving the `Tracking/TrackBuilding` from trackingOnly client to standard client.

Tested in 9_3_0_pre5, expecting efficiency, fake rate etc. histograms under `Tracking/TrackBuilding`, no changes expected in any existing histogram.

@rovere @VinInn @ebrondol
